Aku berhasil.

134
00:13:17,890 --> 00:13:18,740
Masih ada lagi!

135
00:13:18,740 --> 00:13:19,690
Baik!

136
00:13:34,210 --> 00:13:39,630
Aku sudah mengakuimu
sebagai temanku, teman kami!

137
00:13:40,170 --> 00:13:41,290
Kami takkan biarkan...

138
00:13:42,430 --> 00:13:43,510
