kau takkan bisa...

159
00:16:06,580 --> 00:16:08,150
Fana.

160
00:16:13,510 --> 00:16:15,460
Fana!

161
00:16:22,690 --> 00:16:26,170
Oh, kau sudah sadar, Mars?

162
00:16:28,170 --> 00:16:29,430
Lotus.

163
00:16:29,430 --> 00:16:31,790
Ya, kerja bagus.

164
