00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:54,830
Aduh, duh, duh.

181
00:17:56,330 --> 00:17:58,640
Baguslah kalau kau baik-
baik saja, Asta Bego.

182
00:17:58,640 --> 00:18:00,640
Sulit dipercaya sekali.

183
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:02,640
Pemulihannya amat luar biasa.

184
