Sakit saja tidak.

207
00:19:10,380 --> 00:19:11,500
Kalian...

208
00:19:13,500 --> 00:19:14,860
Kak Klaus.

209
00:19:16,140 --> 00:19:17,700
Aku benar-benar

210
00:19:19,850 --> 00:19:21,260
minta maaf.

211
00:19:24,430 --> 00:19:29,250
