sobeknya lebar banget.

225
00:20:34,140 --> 00:20:35,080
Mati juga.

226
00:20:35,080 --> 00:20:36,120
Asta!

227
00:20:36,770 --> 00:20:37,920
Aku kelepasan!

228
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:38,970
Asta Bego!

229
00:20:39,450 --> 00:20:40,430
Bertahanlah!

230
00:20:40,430 --> 00:20:41,420
Asta!

231
00:20:51,060 --> 00:20:52,810
Apa lihat-lihat?

232
00:22:43,090 --> 00:22:45,470
Semanggi Kerdil!

233
00:22:46,860 --> 00:22:49,260
Bisa Bilang Begitu Juga Ternyata.

234
00:22:51,630 --> 00:22:52,380
Aku selamat.

